performing its development and management services.", "bbox": [143.8, 1219.9, 1094.0, 1240.7]}, {"text": "During the years ended December 31, 2017, 2016 and 2015, the Company incurred $390 million, $387 million", "bbox": [143.8, 1244.9, 1094.0, 1265.7]}, {"text": "and $393 million, respectively, of costs reimbursable by CityCenter, primarily for employee compensation and", "bbox": [143.8, 1269.9, 1094.2, 1290.7]}, {"text": "certain allocated costs. As of December 31, 2017 and 2016, CityCenter owed the Company $75 million and", "bbox": [143.8, 1294.9, 1094.2, 1315.7]}, {"text": "$77 million, respectively, for management services and reimbursable costs recorded in “Accounts receivable,", "bbox": [143.8, 1319.9, 1094.0, 1340.7]}, {"text": "net” in the accompanying consolidated balance sheets.", "bbox": [143.8, 1344.9, 598.9, 1365.7]}, {"text": "74", "bbox": [609.6, 1465.3, 628.4, 1484.0]}]}